{"name":"Hallowed Ground","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Note to GMs</span></p>\n<p>Yes, the spell mention Wisdom for damage at the initial level (3), then Charisma for damage at higher levels both in the original PDF and on the online SRD.</p>\n<p>For me, it doesn't make sense, so I changed the initial level to CHA to have a more fluid progression (and to not penalize a stat choice). Still, your game, your call, so you should discuss it with the player that takes this spell (e.g. to keep to original attribute choice, or to instead make all damage roll with WIS, although this will make the spell more powerful), then remove this description for the spell on the Cleric char-sheet (to not be spammed each time the spell is used)</p>"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":"Domain: Any"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":3},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"move"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Close-quarters"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"All nearby enemies or the encounter environment (GM’s discretion)"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":"<p>Nearby enemies suffer [[1d10 + @cha.dmg]] holy damage every round until the escalation die equals [[@lvl]] (to a maximum of 6 rounds). A normal save (11+) halves this damage, although demons, devils, and undead must instead make a hard save (16+).</p>\n<p>At the GM&rsquo;s discretion, you can also cast this spell to eliminate a single environmental effect of your tier or lower which bolsters demons, devils, or undead, or which deals negative energy damage to you and your allies; the effect is suppressed for the same number of rounds.</p>"},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"[[2d10 + @cha.dmg]] holy damage"},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[4d10 + @cha.dmg]] holy damage"},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[6d10 + @cha.dmg]] holy damage"},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>The spell is now recharge 16+ after battle instead of daily.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>This spell is now a quick action to cast.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"IhuJiKqmWUDQs6PZ"}
