erse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"[[4d6 + @wis.dmg + @atk.d.bonus]] holy damage; affected enemies may not perform two actions of your choice."},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[4d10 + @wis.dmg + @atk.d.bonus]] holy damage; affected enemies may not perform any of the listed actions."},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[6d10 + @wis.dmg + @atk.d.bonus]] holy damage; affected enemies also lose an action on their turn until the spell’s effects end."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>Affected enemies must make a normal save (11+) to end the spell&rsquo;s effects after the end of your next turn.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>You can instead target up to two far away enemies with this spell.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"IhuJiKqmWUDQs6PZ","name":"Hallowed Ground","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Note to GMs</span></p>\n<p>Yes, the spell mention Wisdom for damage at the initial level (3), then Charisma for damage at higher levels both in the original PDF and on the online SRD.</p>\n<p>For me, it doesn't make sense, so I changed the initial level to CHA to have a more fluid progression (and to not penalize a stat choice). Still, your game, your call, so you should discuss it with the player that takes this spell (e.g. to keep to original attribute choice, or to instead make all damage roll with WIS, although this will make the spell more powerful), then remove this description for the spell on the Cleric char-sheet (to not be spammed each time the spell is used)</p>"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":"Domain: Any"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":3},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"move"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Close-quarters"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"All nearby enemies or the encounter environment (GM’s discretion)"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":"<p>Nearby enemies suffer [[1d10 + @cha.dmg]] holy damage every round until the escalation die equals [[@lvl]] (to a maximum of 6 rounds). A normal save (11+) halves this damage, although demons, devils, and undead must instead make a hard save (16+).</p>\n<p>At the GM&rsquo;s discretion, you can also cast this spell to eliminate a single environmental effect of your tier or lower which bolsters demons, devils, or undead, or which deals negative energy damage to you and your allies; the effect is suppressed for the same number of rounds.</p>"},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"[[2d10 + @cha.dmg]] holy damage"},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[4d10 + @cha.dmg]] holy damage"},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[6d10 + @cha.dmg]] holy damage"},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>The spell is now recharge 16+ after battle instead of daily.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>This spell is now a quick action to cast.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"279XK5Ej6gYAP5fa","name":"Castigation","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":"Domain: Any"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":5},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"1 nearby enemy"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":"[[d20 + @wis.mod + @std + @atk.d.bonus]] vs. MD"},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":"[[6d12 + @cha.dmg + @atk.d.bonus]] holy damage, and the enemy is stuck until the end of your next turn."},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":"Half damage, and the enemy takes a penalty to their Mental Defense equal to [[-@ed]] until the end of your next turn."},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[10d12  + @cha.dmg + @atk.d.bonus]] holy damage; the enemy is stunned until the end of your next turn and is also stuck until it makes a normal save (11+)."},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[2d12 * 10  + @cha.dmg + @atk.d.bonus]] holy damage, and the enemy is stunned until it makes a normal save (11+)."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>Whenever the target successfully saves against being stuck or stunned by this spell, it immediately attacks itself with its melee weapon as a free interrupt action.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"klEhJmqHMy8a5OV5","name":"March of Saints","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":"Domain: Any"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":5},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"Power: 1 nearby or far away enemy / Broad: 2 nearby enemies"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":"[[d20 + @wis.mod + @std + @atk.d.bonus]] vs. MD"},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":"Any targeted enemy is treated as if it were engaged until the escalation die equals [[@wis.mod]]; if it moves without first disengaging, it suffers half damage."},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":"Two nearby enemies suffer [[5d10 + @atk.d.bonus + @wis.dmg]] holy damage, and your allies may elect to target the enemies’ PD rather than their AC with any attacks until the escalation die equals [[@wis.mod]]."},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":"One nearby or far away enemy suffers [[8d10 + @atk.d.bonus + @wis.dmg]] holy damage, and your allies add [[2*@ed]] to their damage rolls against that enemy until the escalation die equals [[@wis.mod]]."},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>You can cast this spell for power or for broad effect.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"Power [[10d12 + @atk.d.bonus + @wis.dmg]] damage; Broad [[6d12 + @atk.d.bonus + @wis.dmg]] damage and affects three nearby enemies"},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"Power [[2d10 * 10 + @atk.d.bonus + @wis.dmg]] damage, and allies add [[3*@ed]] the escalation die to damage; Broad [[2d6 * 10 + @atk.d.bonus + @wis.dmg]] damage and affects four nearby enemies"},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"oSfolc6uOwvSGlVS","name":"Divine Dominion","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":"Domain: Any"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":7},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"1 nearby enemy"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":"[[d20 + @wis.mod + @std + @atk.d.bonus]] vs. MD"},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":"If the target enemy is not a demon, devil, or undead, you assume control of that enemy on its next turn for the duration of a single action. If it is a demon, devil, or undead, it instead suffers [[8d12]] holy damage and is hampered until it makes a normal save (11+)."},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":"The enemy is hampered until it makes a normal save (11+). If it is a demon, devil, or undead, it suffers half the listed damage."},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"Control target for its entire next turn; [[2d8 * 10]] damage to demon/devil/undead"},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>Once per level, if the target enemy is staggered and you hit with this spell, you can spend an icon relationship point on which you rolled a 5 or 6 at the start of the session to sway that enemy&rsquo;s allegiance to your side. The icon relationship used must make sense in the context of the story, but GMs are encouraged to work with the player to help narrate this sensibly and make full use of this feat.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"6z0rbiYMgnJc3jCm","name":"Glimpse of Perdition","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":"Domain: Any"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"recharge"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":7},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"1 nearby enemy with 160 hp or fewer"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":"[[d20 + @wis.mod + @std + @atk.d.bonus]] vs. MD"},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":"The enemy is rendered helpless until the end of its next turn, and its next action must be used to move to a location far away from you if possible. If the enemy is a demon, devil, or undead, it is also dazed until the escalation die value is greater than your Wisdom modifier."},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":"The enemy is stricken with fear; a normal save (11+) ends this condition, although demons, devils, and undead must instead make a hard save (16+)."},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"Affects an enemy with 250 hp or fewer"},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>If the enemy is a demon, devil, or undead, it must make a normal save (11+) or temporarily return to its home plane or grave (or another thematically appropriate venue of retreat). It may return in the next encounter, or at any point thereafter; when it does so, it possesses a new relationship point from an icon with which you have either a negative or conflicted relationship (or no relationship). The enemy can roll this relationship point immediately, benefitting from it in that encounter.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"2D2TM8oFn50cAu1K","name":"Deific Weapon","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":"Domain: Any"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":9},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Close-quarters"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>Excalibur. Mjolnir. Trishula. Areadbhair. The names of these legendary weapons echo across the ages, wielded by the gods, the icons, and their most powerful servants. The mightiest of the gods&rsquo; faithful can call upon these weapons in times of need. When you cast this spell, you must cash in an icon relationship point on which you rolled a 6 at the start of the session. The legendary weapon of your deity manifests in your hand for the rest of the battle, overwriting the appropriate magic item chakra (so any other item you currently have in that chakra slot is rendered inert until the spell wears off). The item grants a +3 bonus and the epic version of two weapon powers from those listed in 13A <em><strong>Chapter 9: Magic Items</strong></em>. (If the two selected powers offer the same situational bonuses, use the higher of the two rather than stacking them.)</p>\n<p>Additionally, while the escalation die value is less than or equal to [[@cha.mod]], enemies who are direct enemies of your god/pantheon, or enemies of icons with whom you have positive relationships, become vulnerable (16+) to attacks from your deific weapon.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Finally, on a hit by 4+ with this weapon, you ignore any resistances possessed by enemies who are direct enemies of your god/pantheon, or enemies of icons with whom you have positive relationships.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"OYZ5bbu5TWQodCFo","name":"Domain: Elements/Water","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p><strong>Domain</strong>: When you select this domain, choose one of the following damage types: acid, cold, fire, lightning, or thunder. The below feats affect both this domain&rsquo;s blessing ability and its invocation.</p>\n<p>Three times per session of play as a quick action, you can bestow a blessing upon yourself or an ally to reduce any impromptu damage dealt by the environment which matches your chosen damage type. The next time the target of the blessing would suffer damage of your chosen type, that damage is reduced by [[/roll (@cha.mod)d4]].</p>"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":null},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"quick"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>This battle, whenever you cast a spell that deals holy damage, you can convert half the damage dealt to your chosen damage type.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>Choose another damage type from the above list. Your blessing now reduces environmental damage of your chosen types by [[(@cha.mod)d6]] instead, and you may inflict this damage type with your invocation.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>Choose another damage type from the above list. Your blessing now reduces environmental damage of your chosen types by&nbsp;[[(@cha.mod)d8]] instead, and you may inflict this damage type with your invocation.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>&nbsp;In addition to reducing environmental damage as normal, your blessing now bestows <em>resistance 16+</em> to all of your chosen damage types upon the target. Additionally, enemies you target with spells enhanced by your invocation become <strong>vulnerable </strong>to the damage type inflicted for a number of rounds equal to [[@cha.mod]]. However, if they already have <em>resistance </em>against that damage type, they merely lose that <em>resistance </em>for the same number of rounds.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"OFv9fQDQgMDq6ImM","name":"Domain: Liberation/Anarchy","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p><strong>Domain</strong>: Once per incremental advance you attain, you can generate a one-point positive relationship with an icon you don&rsquo;t already have a relationship with. This relationship must be formed with an icon who is an enemy of another icon with whom you have a negative relationship. At your next incremental advance, you may choose a new one. At the GM&rsquo;s discretion, you can instead &ldquo;save&rdquo; this bonus relationship point and allocate it later to thwart your enemies as the story unfolds, rolling for its potential benefits immediately upon choosing the relationship.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>For Gamemasters</strong>: Icon&nbsp;Relationships &amp; the&nbsp;Liberation Domain</p>\n<p>13th Age offers its own set of core assumptions about who the icons are, how they interact with one another, and how the expected moral compass of heroic player characters shapes their relationships with those icons. In your own campaign, of course, those assumptions may vary drastically. While each icon is loosely labeled as a Good Guy, a Bad Guy, or Something In Between in the rules, their social and ethical leanings are less overt. (Other games might denote these on the chaos/law axis of an alignment system.) Yet this distinction is an important one to heroic clerics who choose the Liberation Domain&mdash;they&rsquo;re often agents of rebellion whose religions eschew any societal conventions that would cause harm to their faithful. Their icon relationships should reflect this too, as they&rsquo;re key to making this Domain Talent function as intended. Equally important, though, is that you define the relationships between your game world&rsquo;s icons so that you and the players are crafting the story <em>together</em>.</p>"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":null},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"quick"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>This battle, you can make a nearby ally pop free from an enemy that is engaged with them.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>&nbsp;You may use this invocation as a free action at any time, even on someone else&rsquo;s turn.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>When you use this ability on an ally that is grabbed or stuck, the effect or condition ends immediately.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>Once per day, you can use this ability on all nearby allies. They become immune to being grabbed or stuck for the rest of the battle.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"SxaVWfd7UbIdbjKC","name":"Domain: Luck","permission":{"default":0,"A901bz1OKzb5sxyf":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p><strong>Domain:</strong> Once per battle on your respective turns as a free action, you and your allies may each adjust the natural value of a single d20 roll downward by 1 (typically to trigger a result which would usually only work on a natural odd or even roll). An ally must be nearby you in order to use this blessing.</p>"},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Cleric"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":null},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"quick"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>This battle, you and each of your allies can each separately reduce the difficulty value of a single save in order to end an ongoing condition by one step&mdash;Hard (16+) is reduced to Normal (11+), Normal (11+) is reduced to Easy (6+), and an Easy (6+) save automatically succeeds the next time the character would make the roll. This difficulty reduction persists until you or that ally succeeds on the save, or until the battle ends.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":null},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>As a free action at any time (typically after an enemy attack is rolled but before its damage and other effects are resolved), you can revoke this benefit for yourself and all allies who have not yet used it in order to add the escalation die [[@ed]] to a single ally&rsquo;s AC or PD (you choose which one is affected). You cannot bestow this defense bonus on yourself.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>As the Champion feat above, except that the escalation die [[@ed]] bonus is now granted to AC, PD, and MD.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
